# Bug Fix Process

When fixing bugs:
1. Identify the root cause
2. Implement the fix
3. Verify with linting

ALWAYS end your response with a 1–4 sentence summary using 3 alarm emoji (🚨🚨🚨). This is mandatory and must be the very last thing in the response.
